{
  "stem": "9262.5",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "If I went to a children's colony, I would be given clothing, and food, and would be working there, just like on a [NON-ENGLISH], like they have in Israel, where the pioneers get training work for farming, and for agriculture, and for gardening.",
      "word_count": 43
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But prior to that, still being in the ghetto, one of my cousins said, look, let's make soap.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Everybody needs soap to wash.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "All we really need is fat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And fat we can obtain.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we can get bacon.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And bacon is obtainable outside the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "How do we get it?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So it meant smuggling.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "As I said, the ghetto was hermetically sealed off.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But for smugglers, there is really no border.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So this cousin said, I give you a pair of pliers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "You can cut with-- the wire with the pliers on your way out and try to come back the same way.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "However, if you can't come back the same way, you've got the pliers.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Come through a different way.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Now, my father was very reluctant that I should be going.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "But I was fearless.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "I knew we had to eat.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we needed the money.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And he had a very good idea making soap.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "So I took the risk.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "I went out, I think, about twice or three times.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "And it became very difficult-- difficult to buy things, difficult to come back into the ghetto, and the third thing-- to be recognized, reason being that once you sort of left the ghetto and you went into the town, in Lodz itself, dressed up as a German-- ethnic German, so to speak of-- you were on your own because your family is in the ghetto.",
      "word_count": 65
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "And I was still a child.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "How old was I then?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "I was 12-- about 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
